Maximum flow - Dinic's algorithm
Dinic's algorithm solves the maximum flow problem in . The maximum flow problem is defined in this article Maximum flow - Ford-Fulkerson and Edmonds-Karp. This algorithm was discovered by Yefim Dinitz in 1970.
Definitions
A residual network  of network  is a network which contains two edges for each edge :

